{"tid":869752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[老當益壯] 雲加穿4號落場踢足一個鐘中堅, 一齊睇片","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T14:21:38.000Z","uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"123a29a7814b6cf0c087b004c4028a531435f433","tid":869752,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DK-SJaWzpKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDK-SJaWzpKQ&d=615rysS2UWjGrm1Hpz%2F2djQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=901d07ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DK-SJaWzpKQ</a><br />\n<br />\n前阿仙奴領隊雲格的執教功力如何，球迷們各有看法，不過要在芸芸領隊中，雲格一直被公認為腳法較好的一位，過去網上不時流出一些他在訓練場上展示腳法的影片，日前他就參與一場慈善球賽，不但有份落場獻技，更踢了一個小時，讓球迷們大飽眼福。<br />\n<br />\n這場慈善賽在法國東部紅酒名區勃艮第的桑拉維爾球場舉行，有超過一萬名觀眾入場，現年 68 歲的雲格在球員時代擔任中場，不過今場比賽他卻穿上「 4 」球衣出任中堅角色，除了他之外，法國前國腳迪甘斯、白蘭斯等人也有參與這場慈善賽，與當地球隊 Gueugnon 的元老隊比賽，最終雲格踢了 60 分鐘，雙方以 5 比 5 打成平手，和氣收場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:45 佢招牌動作<br />\n<img src=\"http://en.espn.co.uk/PICTURES/CMS/63700/63745.3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.espn.co.uk%2FPICTURES%2FCMS%2F63700%2F63745.3.jpg&h=0783eb64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e8287c6fcd6a14797e78f70968566b7d1870947","tid":869752,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9750ef066f33181f39f2643f5eb403066940aa4a","tid":869752,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"前4狂魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419ca2d990946b3f428bb757a6129b4d85c7db86","tid":869752,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}